<div class="gal-intro">
  <span class="section-label">The Work</span>
  <p>Over 16 years of aerosol culture, digital creation, and immersive visual transformation. Every piece on these walls started with a blank surface and a vision &mdash; whether that surface was a building, a canvas, or a screen.</p>
</div>

<div class="gal-filters">
  <button class="gf active">All Work</button>
  <button class="gf">Murals</button>
  <button class="gf">Portraits</button>
  <button class="gf">Wildstyle</button>
  <button class="gf">Digital</button>
  <button class="gf">Commercial</button>
</div>

<div class="gal-masonry">
  <div class="gal-item wide">
    <img src="{{ 'lb-blueprint-gallery-011.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Lacquer Bru wildstyle mural" loading="lazy">
    <div class="gal-item-ov">
      <div class="gal-item-title">Wildstyle &mdash; Group Production</div>
      <div class="gal-item-cat">Graffiti &middot; Mural</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="gal-item">
    <img src="{{ 'lb-blueprint-gallery-012.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Portrait mural" loading="lazy">
    <div class="gal-item-ov">
      <div class="gal-item-title">Portrait Study</div>
      <div class="gal-item-cat">Portrait &middot; Mural</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="gal-item">
    <img src="{{ 'lb-blueprint-gallery-013.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Fire mural" loading="lazy">
    <div class="gal-item-ov">
      <div class="gal-item-title">Fire &amp; Motion</div>
      <div class="gal-item-cat">Character &middot; Mural</div>
    </div>
  </div>
