    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="gal-cta">
  <span class="section-label">Commission Your Own Piece</span>
  <h2 class="section-h2">See Something You Like?</h2>
  <p>Every wall, canvas, and surface is an opportunity. Get in touch to discuss your project and let us create something original together.</p>
  <a href="https://lacquerbru.co.za/commission-inquiry" class="btn-primary">Start a Commission</a>
</div>




</section>

